docs/AI-*.md export-ignore
docs/PROMPT-*.md export-ignore
CLAUDE.md export-ignore

# Language statistics (GitHub)
vendor/* linguist-vendored
public/admin/assets/* linguist-vendored
*.min.js linguist-vendored
